            <title><![CDATA[Borderlands 4 Will Push Franchise Beyond 100 Million Sales, Gearbox CEO Says]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/borderlands-4-will-push-franchise-beyond-100-million-sales-gearbox-ceo-says/1100-6534199/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
